---

<MainLayout
  title="Metal Roof Installation in Temple, Killeen & Central Texas | Lone Ranger Roofing"
  description="Lone Ranger Roofing installs standing seam, metal shingle, and R-panel metal roofs across Temple, Killeen, and Central Texas. We fabricate panels on-site with our own machine. Financing available."
  darkHero={true}
>

  <!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[65vh] flex items-center bg-brand-900 overflow-hidden -mt-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/home-roof-replacement.webp"
        alt="Metal roof installation in Temple and Killeen TX"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-900 via-brand-900/85 to-brand-900/30"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 py-28">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Residential Roofing &rsaquo; Metal Roofing</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Metal Roof Installation in Temple, Killeen &amp; Central Texas
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          The last roof you'll ever put on your house. We fabricate panels on-site with our own machine so your project never stalls waiting on a supplier.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 text-white font-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center shadow-lg">
            Get a Free Metal Roof Estimate
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+12543001413" class="border-2 border-white/50 hover:border-white text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center hover:bg-white/10">
            Call (254) 300-1413
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust bar -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 mt-10">
          {[
            'On-Site Fabrication Machine',
            'Material + Labor Warranty',
            'Financing Available',
          ].map(t => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              {t}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== ON-SITE MACHINE ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <!-- Photo side -->
        <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="/fab1.webp"
            alt="Lone Ranger Roofing on-site metal panel fabrication — Central Texas"
            class="w-full h-[480px] object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 bg-brand-900 text-white rounded-xl p-5 max-w-[230px] shadow-xl border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">What On-Site Fabrication Means For You</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5">
              {[
                'Panels cut to exact measurements on-site',
                'No supplier delays if dimensions change',
                'Faster project completion',
                'Better fit, cleaner finish',
                'Less time with your home exposed',
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-brand-200 text-xs leading-snug">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-accent-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Text side -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">On-Site Fabrication</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-6">
            We Own Our Own Fabrication Machine. Here's Why That Matters to You.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Most metal roofing contractors order panels from a supplier. That means if a measurement is off, if something ships wrong, or if the supplier runs short — your project stops. You wait. Your home sits exposed.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Lone Ranger Roofing owns our own metal panel fabrication machine. We cut panels to exact specifications on-site. If a measurement needs to change, we adjust and cut right there. No reordering. No waiting on a truck. No prolonged projects because a supplier got the dimensions wrong.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            For homeowners in Temple, Killeen, Harker Heights, Belton, and across Central Texas and DFW, that means a cleaner install, a faster turnaround, and a finished roof that fits exactly the way it should.
          </p>
